{"tid":816234,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係邊撚個發明埋D垃圾自動感應沖水??","createTime":"2018-09-12T15:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T02:36:48.000Z","uid":186152,"like":598,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9f2da4d621e1d8843f1717fb26f9243a701ee3","tid":816234,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:11:41.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母正常柯屎前都會拎幾格廁紙抹下廁板先<br />\n再掉埋落屎坑用黎防止彈水花<br />\n但係一坐落去已經自動感應沖撚左水<br />\n然後D廁紙沖走晒再有沖水水花彈到屎忽<br />\n再柯舊屎落去又彈水花<br />\n拎部電話出黎上下連登打下字回覆<br />\n諗住個人傾前少少隻手可以埃住膝頭舒服D<br />\n然後又沖水再彈D有屎既屎水水花上黎我屎忽<br />\n跟撚住真係嬲撚到想一拳打鳩爆個感應器<br />\n依家仲要越黎越多商場係用自動感應器沖水<br />\n我屌你老母如果比我知道邊個發明埋呢D垃圾感應器<br />\n我真係會斬撚死你條仆街"},{"pid":"760d9128b31f478d94079218fb9c6d06fb373fb9","tid":816234,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":142,"score":-135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68bc697ec91ca38dda3537f8e1a48e18a5220ec9","tid":816234,"uid":186152,"like":236,"dislike":5,"score":231,"quote":{"pid":"760d9128b31f478d94079218fb9c6d06fb373fb9","tid":816234,"uid":208726,"like":7,"dislike":142,"score":-135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"最好應該用黎沖鳩你老母個閪"},{"pid":"8e9a8a68f9d88fa8c5328f24e3ebe9ba0fb12395","tid":816234,"uid":208726,"like":6,"dislike":91,"score":-85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"526741e593a8d1c834b40f1ae59f57570c35a5fb","tid":816234,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"mtr全部都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a35419f2ba5904b5729fd21d7e84